D. MAIN STUDIO: Licensees are required to maintain a meaningful management and staff presence at stations, even when they are engaged in an LMA.
The Commission has interpreted this to mean full-time managerial and full-time staff personnel are to be employed and present at the station during normal business hours.
[See 73.1125]
